data.description: STOP THE CAR!!! PRICE REDUCED!!! This is the Ranch you've been waiting for! Spectacular views out every large window! Light, Bright and Airy 4 bedroom homes with spacious rooms. Entertainers delight. Large Master bedroom with walk out to deck, Full bath, walk in closet and additional closets.  Amazing kitchen offers cabinets galore and Center Island, 2 large pantries and sliders to deck from eating area. Full unfinished basement with walk out and roughed for bath waiting to be finished to enhance the endless opportunities to this galore home. Relax on the back deck while enjoying the breathtaking views nature offers or sit by the pond and get lost in the beauty of country living. Over 14 acres of property keeps you private and set back from the road to enjoy everything.
